Update tutorial for python3

Updated tutorial to run with python3 library
Also added a sample of how to load and read SVG files.

Fix SVG Parsing issues

Ignore empty lines and empty text elements inside svg
and fix uppercasing code

Closes https://github.com/alorence/pysvg-py3/issues/3

Bump to version 0.2.2-post2

rev1 suffix has been replaced by post2, to conform with PEP 440. See https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0440/#post-release-separators
